<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-02 13:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8533 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-TV-DVR-ART-BOS &LR;      09-02 1488
