<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-02 16:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8748 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-ANIMALS-FILM-REVIEW-N     09-02 0896
