   FILM-CHOCOLATE &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ It's odd that men have always been perceived as the
more sex-obsessed gay gender, especially when the new lesbian
comedy ``Better Than Chocolate'' has more blush-inducing moments
than the gay-themed ``Get Real,'' ``Edge of Seventeen,'' ``Trick''
and the upcoming ``Steam'' combined. In fact, ``Chocolate'' may
hold the record for most ``marital aids'' displayed in a feature
film; maybe that'll wind up as a category on the MTV Movie Awards.
By TODD CAMP. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
