</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Although wariness about giving out personal
information can be carried to extremes, it does pay to err on the
side of excess caution in that regard rather than not enough. A
case in point is the man who dumped his garbage bags on my curb the
other day. You heard me right: This guy in a pickup just drives up
and offloads two plastic bags of refuse on the curb next to mine.
By CECIL JOHNSON. Story has moved in ``k'' commentary category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
nn
</P>
