 Here is an updated budget for the Focus and Nascar Pages. Focus
will be available by 5 p.m. Friday, Sept. 3, 1999. Nascar will be
available by 5 p.m. Thursday, Sept. 2, 1999. For questions call
CoxNet at (404) 526-5456.
