when they line up at Darlington this weekend? NASCAR history
suggests that Dale Earnhardt, who wrecked Labonte on the final lap
at Bristol last week, might want to tighten his rearview mirrors.
(Includes a 3-column color photo of Terry Labonte and one 2-column
color photo of Dale Earnhardt.)
</P>
