<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    A&AMP;M will introduce calf cloned from adult bovine
 &HT;    By Mary Ann Roser
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
