<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    DEWINE ENDORSES MCCAIN FOR PRESIDENT
 &HT;    330&AMP;add. Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT MONTGOMERY
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
