<SLUG> BC-NY-POLICE-SHOOTING-MENTAL-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MAN SLAIN BY POLICE FEARED OWN VIOLENT IMPULSES, RECORDS SHOW 
</HEADLINE>
   (bl)  
 By JULIAN E. BARNES and SUSAN SACHS   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ The Brooklyn man fatally shot by police Monday had
